{
  "title": "Funky Mexican Chicken Grill",
  "description": "This dish is a twist on traditional Mexican cuisine, with the addition of Massaman curry paste for a unique and funky flavor. It's perfect for a cozy night in, and is also flexitarian-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Mexican",
