  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together curry paste, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add olive oil to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Add lime juice and stir to combine.",
    "Add garlic to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Place chicken breasts on the grill and cook for 5-7 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "While chicken is cooking, brush red bell pepper and red onion slices with some of the curry paste mixture and grill for 3-5 minutes per side, or until tender.",
    "Once chicken is cooked, brush with remaining curry paste mixture and serve with grilled vegetables and cilantro."
